Veldt reuses components (the now-playing overlay/pill and the media-session
plumbing) from Veldt Wisp, which is itself a fork of DynamicIslandMusic. It is
distributed under the license below, inherited from the upstream project. The
original copyright notice and attribution requirement are retained in full, as
that license requires.

